FBIS4-58969 "drnes090_j_94024" FBIS-NES-94-090 Daily Report 10 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen New Defense Minister Takes Oath New Defense Minister Takes Oath JN1005131794 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1200 GMT 10 May 94 JN1005131794 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Brother Brigadier General 'Abd-Rabbuh Mansur Hadi, the minister of defense, today took the constitutional oath before brother Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, chairman of the Presidential Council and supreme commander of the Armed Forces, on his appointment as defense minister.
